title: Comedy Nights with Kapil - Ranbir Kapoor & Pallavi Sharda -
description:
The hilarious episode starts with Kapil's entry who wants get rid of Daadi's addiction of alcohol. Later, Bua brings Kiku as Baba Bengali as he is well versed in rehabilitating people's addictions. Baba Bengali does all his attempts to restore Daadi's health. Ranbir Kapoor and Pallavi Sharda come to the show to promote their upcoming movie, Besharam. Watch the entire episode to witness Ranbir Kapoor show his sense of humor.
Renowned, actor-comedian Kapil Sharma makes his debut as a TV show producer with his new show Comedy Nights With Kapil. He will be seen multiple roles of an actor, scriptwriter and producer in his production debut. Already famous for his amazing comic timing and his talent to dig humor out of any situation, he is ready present everyday life in a fresh ad unique way.
